message.text:
LRT Line 2 Santolan Station has temporarily suspended operations due to issues with the railway and train at Santolan Station.

However, service between Recto and Araneta Center-Cubao stations (and vice versa) remains operational. 

The public is advised to take alternative means of transportation while provisional service is ongoing. 

Light Rail Transit Authority (LRTA) Administrator Atty. Hernando Cabrera said, full line operation may resume within the day subject to the clearance of the safety officers on site.| via Darylle Marie Sarmiento, ABS-CBN News

message.text:
LRT Line 2 Santolan Station has temporarily suspended operations due to issues with the railway and train at Santolan Station.

However, service between Recto and Araneta Center-Cubao stations (and vice versa) remains operational. 

The public is advised to take alternative means of transportation while provisional service is ongoing. 

Light Rail Transit Authority (LRTA) Administrator Atty. Hernando Cabrera said, full line operation may resume within the day subject to the clearance of the safety officers on site.| via Darylle Marie Sarmiento, ABS-CBN News

message.text:
LRT Line 2 Santolan Station has temporarily suspended operations due to issues with the railway and train at Santolan Station.

However, service between Recto and Araneta Center-Cubao stations (and vice versa) remains operational. 

The public is advised to take alternative means of transportation while provisional service is ongoing. 

Light Rail Transit Authority (LRTA) Administrator Atty. Hernando Cabrera said, full line operation may resume within the day subject to the clearance of the safety officers on site.| via Darylle Marie Sarmiento, ABS-CBN News
